headline: UATP LAUNCHES SETTLEMENT SOLUTION IN INDIA
summary: UATP, the global network that enables organizations to simplify payment processes to expand their payment capabilities, has partnered with fintech companies (licensed in India) to launch a new settlement solution. Through this partnership, contractors with customers using UATP accounts will be able to settle air ticket purchases in Indian Rupees (INR), enabling ticketors like airlines to be funded in the INR currency.
